/#
 When a requested option exercise event is desired to be performed.
 #/
enum FpML5.recordkeeping.ExerciseTimingEnum {
    # Perform the requested exercise behavior immediately on receipt of the request.
    Immediate 
    # Perform the requested exercise behavior at the expiration of the option.
    OnExpiration 

}

Immediate.Doc: Perform the requested exercise behavior immediately on receipt of the request.
Immediate.Name: Immediate

OnExpiration.Doc: Perform the requested exercise behavior at the expiration of the option.
OnExpiration.Name: OnExpiration
